Class Junction

  • java.lang.Object
    • Junction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Junction>

    public class Junction
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Junction>
    This class serves as the generic node class which will act as a junction, these junctions can serve as "traffic" junctions in which only traffic passes through, or it can serve as a junction with a Restaurant or Farm.
    Author:
    Craig Lombardo
